<lb n="6"/>dīpamunakuṁ beṭṭina birudumāḍalu paṁḍreṁḍu vīniṁ jēkoni yiṁdu
<lb n="7" break="no"/>la dēvagarmmi bhāvarāju koḍuku gōka <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> pavitrikamu nitya māneṁḍu ne
